# Large raw data files (>50MB) - git has no automatic size filter, so this project's own
# small per-album CSVs under data/raw/ and data/processed/ are intentionally NOT excluded here
# (they're deliverables). This only catches generic large-archive formats if they show up.
*.csv.gz
*.parquet
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Logs
*.log

# Locally-owned copyrighted audio files, used only for local librosa feature extraction.
# Never committed — this is personal-use source audio, not something to redistribute
# through a public repo, regardless of how it was legally obtained.
OR-3/
*.mp3
*.wav
*.flac
*.m4a
*.aac
